{"word":"λᾶας","slug":"λᾶας","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λᾶας</b></el> <el>(λᾶας, ου, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>a <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <el>λάου</el> in <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b> as if <a href='S:λᾶας'><el>λᾶας</el></a> was of first decl.\n<p/><a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>lapis, a stone</el>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/>"}]}